    <briefdescription>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>This device driver is used to add a FIFO read buffer to a device. When writing the FIFO, the device is written directly. Any data that arrives asynchronously through the device is stored in the FIFO buffer. When reading the FIFO, the FIFO buffer is read. </para>    </detaileddescription>
